Compliance & Governance: Ensure all compensation programs comply with federal, state, and local laws, including FLSA, pay transparency regulations, and equal pay laws.

Communication & Training: Educate managers and employees on compensation philosophy, programs, and practices to enhance transparency and understanding.
Process & Technology Implementation: Identify and implement tools or systems to streamline compensation administration and analytics.
